      "review_summary": "The PR exports the hard-timeout phase predicate, updates `waitForAgentJob` to forward pending hard-timeout snapshots from its outer fallback timer, and adds fake-timer gateway/agent regression coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +13, Tests +155. Total +168 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current `main` stores pending timeout snapshots but the outer `waitForAgentJob` fallback still returns only pending errors or `null`. I did not run a fresh live parent/subagent timeout in this read-only review.",
